entries.title_d: Be the middle man for an Imperial exchange
entries.title: Yavin System: Deliver Imperial Goods
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Head out on a quick patrol, seperation from the Transport will help to confuse the Rebels. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_dock2_d: Pull up near the transport and use the /dock command to deliver the cargo
entries.quest_dock1_d: Pull up close to the Freighter and use the /dock command to pick up the cargo
entries.hello_p: Hail Captain, close in for docking.
entries.hello_d: Do not delay, Rebel attack is eminent.
entries.found_loc_p: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 I'm sending you to the Imperial Freighter, they will finish instructions there. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc_d: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Rendezvous location locked in. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_started_pickup: We are transfering over some encrypted material.  This sensitive information, expect some Rebel interference.  Most will come after me, but you will not have an easy run. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_started_delivery: Get this transfer done quickly, we can't staty stationary for long.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: That is all of it.  We have an Imperial transport waiting for you across the zone, I'll upload their location to you.  Good luck.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: All right, this is what we needed.  Now get out of here, you seem to attract Rebels.
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile activity has ceased. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_pickup: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated rendezvous location reached. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated rendezvous location reached. \#pcontrast3 >
